        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "定义一个表达式的开销 (cp)=其所有子表达式的开销 + 其本身的开销。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                184,
                275,
                821,
                293
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 加法的开销是 1，乘法的开销是2，顺序操作的开销是0，如 (a+E).cp= 1 + a.cp + E.cp"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                184,
                297,
                850,
                335
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 赋值的开销是1，还包括作为右值的子表达式的开销。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                186,
                340,
                707,
                357
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 循环的开销是3，还包括循环中每一次迭代的子表达式开销，即子表达式.cp * 循环次数 + 3。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                186,
                361,
                850,
                400
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 每一个变量id与常量int作为表达式的开销均为1。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                186,
                404,
                697,
